/-
MiniLimitColimit — Limits and colimits in category theory
Aggregates all submodules.

Knowledge Coverage:
- L1: Diagram, Cone, Cocone, Limit, Colimit, ConeCat, CoconeCat
- L2: ConeMorphism, IsLimit, IsColimit, IsProduct, IsCoproduct
- L3: Complete/Cocomplete categories, Filtered colimits
- L4: Limit uniqueness (proved), SetCat completeness, limit from products+equalizers
